{"tid":1226393,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企簡直就好似宜家香港狀況","createTime":"2019-06-15T11:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T15:55:13.000Z","uid":209422,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"db56ac80b58dba2f41d8ab2982afedd1b90c91c9","tid":1226393,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:23:18.000Z","msg":"係呢啲非常時期，有感而發講下家事<br />\n<br />\n我<span style=\"color: red;\">老母</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">林鄭</span>佢兩個簡直一模一樣，成鳩日做埋曬啲on9野，原全唔撚理啱定唔啱<br />\n<br />\n當你想同佢理性和平討論，佢就即刻發爛咋，完全唔聽你講，就好似林鄭<span style=\"color: red;\">閉門完全唔理民意，一意孤行</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">又一路當自己好啱</span>，查實成件事就有更好嘅方法，不過佢都係繼續不理會<br />\n<br />\n到佢發爛咋越嚟越激，就出手打你，<span style=\"color: red;\">十足十班警犬速龍</span>，我又冇可能還拖只能一味擋<br />\n<br />\n頭先就又發生狀況，佢又一味屌鳩我，大家冇理性討論，咁啱佢就播新聞台播緊林鄭，我即刻話<span style=\"color: red;\">：「你同林鄭冇分別呀唔撚聽人講」</span>佢當下猶豫咗一下，感覺好似冇講錯，然後<span style=\"color: red;\">佢決定繼續林鄭落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我係屋企可以繼續屈服係呢啲無理狀況下，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但香港絕對唔得，聽日老撚都出嚟遊行，撤回逃犯條例</span>，只要一日唔撤回，我次次都出<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">我老母應該都出，不過唔同佢行</span>"},{"pid":"1122b2a23779e88463e1f34b6a774c7daf75c948","tid":1226393,"uid":145758,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T11:36:22.000Z","msg":"你老母肯出算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我老母：班人收美國佬錢！送返中國有咩唔好？沒有中國香港玩完好耐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41624031d80561c9e705b9e5a00189f9decd52e3","tid":1226393,"uid":209422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s